<h2>Welcome to Rose des Vins! 🎉</h2>

<p>Dear <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>,</p>

<p>Congratulations! Your account has been approved and you now have access to the Rose des Vins platform. We're thrilled to have you join our community of wine enthusiasts.</p>

<div class="success">
    <p><strong>Your account is now active!</strong></p>
</div>

<div class="credentials">
    <h3>🔐 Your Login Credentials</h3>
    <div class="field">
        <strong>Email:</strong> <span>{{email}}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
        <strong>Password:</strong> <span>{{password}}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
        <strong>Domain:</strong> <span>{{domain}}</span>
    </div>
</div>

