    <p><strong>🔒 Security Notice:</strong> For your protection, please change your password after your first login. Your temporary password is only valid for initial access.</p>
</div>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">
        🚀 Login to Your Account
    </a>
</p>

<div class="highlight">
    <p><strong>What's Next?</strong></p>
</div>

